6. Pull Request Approval and Completion Process

1. Create a Pull Request (PR). 

 After committing your changes to the repository, navigate to your Azure DevOps. 

 Create a new pull request from your the latest push or Pull request section.

 Provide a clear description of the changes made in the PR to help reviewers understand the context.



